reviewText: Was a gift for someone else.  They told me they enjoyed the DVD.

Harry Drew is a thoughtful, thorough, and serious researcher, who has spent the time to do this kind of work right.  He has made sure that his data is correct before bringing a conference presentation or releasing information about the Kingman incident.  This DVD is well-worth the time and money if you are interested in an other-than-Roswell investigation.  It's refreshing to see someone with solid academic credentials present this high caliber investigative report.  Highly recommended.
Very interesting investigation. I would recommend it to any I ufo buff. Or even someone with a passing interest.

Excellent treatise on objective discernment and how to pay attention to details. Harry Drew's uncommon love of history and getting it right is beyond refreshing. Been watching this DVD over and over = it never gets old.
I found this video to be packed with info, a very in depth look at the Kingman Crashes by Harry Drew
